<section class="page">
  <div class="wrap narrow legal">
    <span class="eyebrow">Community</span>
    <h1 class="mt-2 mb-3">Community Guidelines</h1>
    <p class="page-lead">A short list that keeps <%= brand.name %> welcoming, respectful, and fun.</p>

    <ol class="mt-3" style="line-height:2;color:var(--muted)">
      <li><strong class="text-gold">Consent first.</strong> Always. Respect a "no" instantly and gracefully.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-gold">Be real.</strong> Authentic profiles and recent photos. No catfishing.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-gold">Be discreet.</strong> What happens between members stays between members. Never share someone's photos or identity.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-gold">Be kind.</strong> No harassment, hate, or body-shaming. Different tastes are welcome; cruelty is not.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-gold">18+ only.</strong> Everyone here is a consenting adult. Report anyone who may not be.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-gold">No selling.</strong> This is a community, not a marketplace. No escorting, solicitation, or spam.</li>
    </ol>

    <p class="muted mt-4">Breaking these can get an account suspended or removed. Help us keep this a great place — <a href="/safety" class="text-gold">report</a> anything that crosses the line.</p>
  </div>
</section>
